{"tid":771811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年金計劃網站故障申請延至明日","createTime":"2018-08-08T09:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T01:01:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0e5ecae96af954f9329cf708529b68df1117dd","tid":771811,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"按揭證券公司旗下香港年金公司推出的「香港年金計劃」，原定今日截止登記認購，但由於年金公司的網站出現技術故障，暫時未能接受認購意向的網上登記，因此網上認購登記將延長一日至明日晚上十一時五十九分止，而代理銀行的收表時間將維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n香港年金公司技術人員正在搶修，務求盡快恢復服務，公司對事件深感抱歉，網站服務恢復後，再作公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_368&amp;itemid=1023386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_368%26itemid%3D1023386&d=AjvRlTjlLkzCUhfqY%2B9748mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a956290e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_368&amp;itemid=1023386</a>"},{"pid":"665485deac93cdd4c4a2fd497fbcbfdebf37e88f","tid":771811,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"由於網站故障 決定開多個星期比大家作為補償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12685457033884533df3b4cee4082379df565f6","tid":771811,"uid":71748,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"無人買就extend"},{"pid":"4e50da1e912d2109e4f6aa0c411de02217aa21a3","tid":771811,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:23:37.000Z","msg":"笑撚左 跑唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e011246bbe77db5bc9c09bd05bd5f192b9e1e60","tid":771811,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"R撈"},{"pid":"d5325813ab7f650dc5f4851fce5ad6a962d19289","tid":771811,"uid":39628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"明天有咩借口再extend?<img src=\"/